CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Tableau - The Physical Activities Department of the YMCA staged a series of exhibitions at the anniversary celebration last Thursday. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Seven members of the Physical Activities Department of the YMCA wearing shorts and metallic paint, preparing for tug of war exhibition on stage for anniversary celebration, audience seated in foreground
